ModuleParameters.Name: R Script
ModuleParameters.Value:
dataset <- maml.mapInputPort(1) 

previous <- 12
orig_names <- names(dataset)
n_rows <- dim(dataset)[1]

base <- 13
for (i in 1:previous) {
  dataset[(i+1):n_rows,base+i] <- dataset[1:(n_rows-i),base]
  dataset[1:i,base+i] <- dataset[1:i,base+i-1]
}

a <- -1:-previous
new_names <- paste("demand in hour",a)
names(dataset) <- c(orig_names,new_names)

maml.mapOutputPort("dataset")

ModuleParameters.Name: R Script
ModuleParameters.Value:
dataset <- maml.mapInputPort(1) 

previous <- 12
orig_names <- names(dataset)
n_rows <- dim(dataset)[1]

base <- 13
for (i in 1:previous) {
  dataset[(i+1):n_rows,base+i] <- dataset[1:(n_rows-i),base]
  dataset[1:i,base+i] <- dataset[1:i,base+i-1]
}

base2 <- base+previous
for (i in 1:previous) {
  dataset[(i*24+1):n_rows,base2+i] <- dataset[1:(n_rows-i*24),base]
  dataset[1:(i*24),base2+i] <- dataset[1:(i*24),base2+i-1] 
}

12 features that are bike demand in the last 12 weeks at the same day and the same hour

ModuleParameters.Name: R Script
ModuleParameters.Value:
dataset <- maml.mapInputPort(1) 

previous <- 12
orig_names <- names(dataset)
n_rows <- dim(dataset)[1]

base <- 13
for (i in 1:previous) {
  dataset[(i+1):n_rows,base+i] <- dataset[1:(n_rows-i),base]
  dataset[1:i,base+i] <- dataset[1:i,base+i-1]
}

base2 <- base+previous
for (i in 1:previous) {
  dataset[(i*24+1):n_rows,base2+i] <- dataset[1:(n_rows-i*24),base]
  dataset[1:(i*24),base2+i] <- dataset[1:(i*24),base2+i-1] 
}

base2 <- base+previous*2
for (i in 1:previous) {
  dataset[(i*24*7+1):n_rows,base2+i] <- dataset[1:(n_rows-i*24*7),base]
  dataset[1:(i*24*7),base2+i] <- dataset[1:(i*24*7),base2+i-1] 
}

a <- -1:-previous
new_names1 <- paste("demand in hour",a)
new_names2 <- paste("demand in day",a)
new_names3 <- paste("demand in week",a)
names(dataset) <- c(orig_names,new_names1,new_names2,new_names3)

maml.mapOutputPort("dataset")

ModuleParameters.Name: R Script

a <- c("baseline: weather + holiday + weekday + weekend features for the predicted day", 
"baseline + previous 12 hours demand",

"baseline + previous 12 hours demand + previous 12 days at the same hour + previous 12 weeks at the same hour and the same day demand")

data.set <- cbind(a, dataset)
names(data.set)[1] <- c("features")
maml.mapOutputPort("data.set")
